request.description:
Create an anonymous user and sign-in into the application. You can choose a unique name for the user. The response will include an authorization token within the `jwt` Cookie.

**Request body scheme**

``` json
{
  // the display name of user
  "name": "Jane Doe" 
}

```

The specified `name` of the user will be trimmed before it gets persisted.

**Request body scheme**

``` json
{
  // the new display name of the user
  "name": "Jane Doe" 
}

```

Create a new board with an initial set of columns. A board session for the calling user will automatically be created on creation of a board.

The access policy can be set to

*   `PUBLIC` if the board should be accessible to everyone by the URL only
*   `BY_PASSPHRASE` if the board should be protected by a passphrase and a challenge before someone is able to join and create a session. If this policy is selected a `passphrase` must be sent as part of the request
*   `BY_INVITE` if the moderators want to manually verify each join request


Currently following color are available for the column accent color:

*   `backlog-blue`
*   `grooming-green`
*   `lean-lilac`
*   `online-orange`
*   `planning-pink`
*   `poker-purple`
*   `retro-red`


**Request body scheme**

``` json
{
  // (optional) board name
  "name": "Awesome collaborative session",
  // the access policy of the board
  "accessPolicy": "BY_PASSPHRASE",
  // (optional) passphrase if the access policy is set as 'BY_PASSPHRASE'
  "passphrase": "***"
  // (optional) array of columns that should be set up initially.
  // The index of the respective columns will be defined by the array position
  "columns": [
    {
      // the name of the column
      "name": "My column name",
      // the visibility state of the column
      "visible": true,
      // the color of the column
      "color": "backlog-blue"
    }
  ]
}

```

**Response body scheme**

``` json
{
  // the uuid (v4) of the created board   
  "id": "a4c93f30-a5ce-4d15-aa5a-92a0ae0831f1",
  // (optional) name of the baord  
  "name": "My board",
  // the access policy of the board
  "accessPolicy": "PUBLIC",
  // flag indicating whether the authors of notes are visible to others
  "showAuthors": true,
  // flag indicating whether the notes are visible between each other
  "showNotesOfOtherUsers": true,
  // flag indicating whether everyone or only moderators allowed to stack cards
  "allowStacking": true,
  // (optional) uuid (v4) of a note which is highlighted to everyone  
  "sharedNote": null,
  // (optional) uuid (v4) of the voting session which results are displayed to everyone
  "showVoting": null
}

```

